OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy low cloud will linger at
OL,6,Ffirst across Wales, but skies will
OL,7,Fgradually brighten through the
OL,8,Fmorning. Some very warm and hazy
OL,9,Fspells of sunshine will develop with
OL,10,Flight winds. Low cloud lingering
OL,11,Faround some coasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAfter a bright and warm
OL,14,Fevening, low cloud will move back in
OL,15,Fovernight to bring mist and fog
OL,16,Fpatches in some areas. Staying dry and
OL,17,Fwarm overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
