OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FLow cloud will burn back
OL,6,Fduring the morning to bring sunny
OL,7,Fskies. Feeling very warm in the
OL,8,Fsunshine and light winds.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,11,FStaying dry and increasingly warm
OL,12,Fthrough the outlook. Plenty of strong
OL,13,Fsunshine and light winds, with some
OL,14,Fwarm nights too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
